⁩ Celebrate the year-end vibes with your squad and welcome the New Year in style! 🎉✨ 

Capture every laugh, every cheer, and every unforgettable memory with Instax. 📸

Because the best moments are meant to be shared. 🌟

Happy New Year 2025 🎊

#InstaxMagic #SquadGoals #YearEndFeels #CaptureEveryMoment #Instax #InstaxIndia #newyear2025

2024 I’ll always remember you!! ❤️❤️

This beautiful year flew by and how.. and as it comes to an end, i feel grateful for everything it brought into my life ❤️.. all the love, happiness, positivity, some amazing people, 3 amazing successes, 4 characters and countless beautiful memories.. 🥰

The audience love for TBMAUJ who made SIFRA even more special for me and made sab kuch “Theek hai”😉 🤖 
3 women killing it at the Boxoffice with CREW brought hope for more films on women being looked at as “commercial” and proving that the audiences love a good film whether it’s driven by men or women!
And the year ended with our first production of @bluebutterflyfilmsofficial DO PATTI getting all the love across borders which still continues to grow.. ❤️🦋

@letshyphen crossing 100cr in a year and @thetribeindia opening another successful branch!!

Couldn’t have asked for anything more ❤️🦋

A big thank you to the audiences and to each and every person who’s been a part of this journey 🙏🏻❤️

I’m excited for an even better 2025!! 🧿🦋
Lets manifest!! 🥰😌
🎄🧑‍🎄 ❤️
